properties.Name: EquifaxCompanyOwner
properties.Description: Returns name, address, phone number, Social Security number and reported date for the business owner, principal or guarantor.

Columns.Name: EfxId
Columns.Description: The EFX ID™ is a unique and persistent nine-digit number that identifies and tracks the business unit with which you have the credit relationship;

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description:
Provides the timestamp when the inquiry was made as recorded
by Equifax (Eastern Time).

Columns.Name: OwnerGuarantorFirstName
Columns.Description: The first name of the  owner/guarantor.

Columns.Name: OwnerGuarantorMiddleName
Columns.Description: The middle name of the  owner/guarantor.

Columns.Name: OwnerGuarantorLastName
Columns.Description: The last name of the  owner/guarantor.

Columns.Name: OwnerGuarantorIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates whether the party is an owner (P), Guarantor (G) or Both (B).

Columns.Name: Address
Columns.Description: The 'street/po box' component of the owner/guarantor's address.

Columns.Name: City
Columns.Description: The 'city' component of the owner/guarantor's address.

Columns.Name: State
Columns.Description: The 'state' component of the owner/guarantor's address.

Columns.Name: ZipCode
Columns.Description: The 'zip code' component of the owner/guarantor's address.

Columns.Name: SocialSecurityNumber
Columns.Description: The social security of the owner/guarantor.

Columns.Name: TaxIdNumber
Columns.Description: The tax ID number of the owner/guarantor.

Columns.Name: SsNumberTaxIdDate
Columns.Description: The date that the SSN or Tax ID Number was provided.
